  "identifier": "cie11cl",
  "description": "Deterministic access to the World Health Organization International Classification of Diseases, 11th Revision (ICD-11, MMS linearization) in Spanish, with code lookup, lexical search, hierarchical navigation, cluster validation, and ICD-10 to ICD-11 crosswalks with traceable certainty levels. The package bundles the WHO MMS 2026 linearization (37,212 entities). The same input plus the same versioned reference data always yields the same output.",
  "name": "cie11cl: ICD-11 (CIE-11) Access and ICD-10 to ICD-11 Crosswalks for Chile",
